SQL_STMT_U.val: select CLNT101_ADMNO, CLNT102_CLNTNO from :1/clnt INNER JOIN :2/CFLC ON CLNT101_ADMNO = CFLC_ADMNOALLOWED AND CLNT102_CLNTNO = CFLC_CLNTNOALLOWED WHERE CFLC_ADMNO=:4 and CFLC_CLNTNO=:5 AND CFLC_USRID=':3' ORDER BY CLNT101_ADMNO, CLNT102_CLNTNO FOR READ ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS

SQL_STMT_U.val: select icph_admno, icph_clntno, icph_bankid, icph_bankaccount,ICPH_BANK_LEDG_NO from :1/icph i where icph_admno=:3 and icph_clntno=:4 and icph_rowtype=1 and icph_bankaccount<>'' and icph_bookingdate>':5' and EXISTS (SELECT * FROM :2/CLBD d where d.CLBD310_ADMNO=i.icph_admno and d.CLBD310_clntno=i.icph_clntno and d.CLBD310_bankid=i.icph_bankid and d.CLBD310_bankaccount LIKE '%' || icph_bankaccount || '%') group by icph_admno, icph_clntno, icph_bankid, icph_bankaccount,ICPH_BANK_LEDG_NO
